Package org.usfirst.frc2084.CMonster2014.commands

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CatcherExtendCommand
    Command that opens the catcher.
    CatcherRetractCommand
    Command that closes the catcher.
    CompressorStartCommand
    Starts the compressor thread.
    CrabLeftCommand
    Command that drives the robot left sideways.
    CrabRightCommand
    Command that drives the robot right sideways.
    DriveCommand
    Command that drives in arcade drive mode.
    FieldCentricMecanumDriveCommand
    The command that implements the control, filtering and scaling of our amazing Mecanum drive system.
    FrontAutonomousCommandGroup
    Runs the autonomous mode where the robot drives forward and expels the ball into the front of the low goal.
    FrontAutonomousDriveAndVisionCommandGroup
    CommandGroup that runs the driving command in parallel with the vision command.
    FrontAutonomousDriveCommand
    Drives the robot forward until it hits the wall.
    FunCommand
    Command that is always running, calculates pi and report debugging values.
    ResetGyroComand
    Command that resets the gyro value to zero.
    SideAutonomousCommandGroup
    DOES NOT WORK! DO NOT USE!
    SideAutonomousDriveCommand
    DOES NOT WORK! DO NOT USE!
    SweeperEjectCommand
    Command that turns on the sweeper motor on so that it pushes the ball out.
    SweeperExtendCommand
    Command that extends the sweeper.
    SweeperOffCommand
    Command that turns on the sweeper motor off.
    SweeperRetractCommand
    Command that retracts the sweeper.
    SweeperSweepCommand
    Command that turns on the sweeper motor on so that it sucks the ball in.
    TimedCommand
    A command that does something once at the beginning but does not finish until a certain time has elapsed.
    WaitForVisionCommand
    This command enables vision processing on the DS laptop and waits for a result.
